;; MECHANISM DESIGN, TRANSFERS, & SIDE PAYMENTS
;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;

(subclass Mechanism Entity)
(documentation Mechanism EnglishLanguage
  "A mapping from reported types, messages, or actions to outcomes and
