(subclass TransferFunction Attribute)
(documentation TransferFunction EnglishLanguage
  "An Attribute describing how a Mechanism assigns monetary or other
   transfers between Players as a function of messages or outcomes.")

(subclass AllocationRule Attribute)
(documentation AllocationRule EnglishLanguage
  "An Attribute describing how a Mechanism maps reports and signals to
